text-tools
==========

This is a small collection of text processing tools.

Installation
------------

  ./autogen.sh   # only if configure doesn't exist yet
  ./configure
  make
  sudo make install

The following commands will be installed:
  texttohtml
  texttopng
  texttops
  texttopdf

They all have man pages.

